---
layout: layouts/default
title: Teaching
description: An overview of workshops I can give at your conference or office and courses from the Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences. I've also made some online courses to learn with me on the web.
permalink: teaching/
---
{% import 'components/atoms/card.njk' as card %}

<h2>Workshops</h2>
<p>I do workshops covering designing for the web for your conference or office.</p>
  <ul class="workshop">
  {% for workshop in workshops.workshops %}
    {{ card.course
      (
        workshop.url,
        workshop.image,
        workshop.title,
        workshop.description,
        workshop.type,
        workshop.length
      )
    }}
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>

<h2>Online Classes</h2>
<p>Learn with me around the web.</p>
  <ul class="workshop">
  {% for item in classes.classes %}
    <article class="project">
    <a href="{{ item.url }}">
      <img src="{{ item.image }}" alt="item Thubmail">
      <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
    </a>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>

<h2>Courses</h2>
<p>These are all the technical courses I give at Communication and Multimedia design at the Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences. Such as Project-tech, front-end, back-end and data visualization.</p>
  <ul class="course">
  {% for item in courses.courses %}
    <article class="project">
    {% include 'components/atoms/corner.njk' %}
    <a href="{{ item.url }}">
      <img src="{{ item.image }}" alt="item Thubmail">
      <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
    </a>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
